Start index: <input type="text" id="startindex" value="" disabled="disabled" /><br />
Profiles sent: <input type="text" id="sent" value="0" disabled="disabled" /><br />
<button id="start">Start loading profiles</button> <button id="stopLoading" disabled="disabled">Stop loading</button>

